    "name": "果宝跑酷: 挑战",
    "steam_appid": 3110420,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一款以跑酷为主线，挑战为支线的卡通休闲动作游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/cef7fc6b2192420aad08c2739b070e1e.poster.avif?t=1731510012\" width=494 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/cef7fc6b2192420aad08c2739b070e1e.webm?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/cef7fc6b2192420aad08c2739b070e1e.mp4?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/439ea0437c767f95841fcef353f097de.poster.avif?t=1731510012\" width=494 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/439ea0437c767f95841fcef353f097de.webm?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/439ea0437c767f95841fcef353f097de.mp4?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏上手简单、难于精通。玩家将扮演一个可爱俏皮的拟人水果宝贝在道路上奔跑，躲避前方不断出现的障碍物，同时收集金币和道具，以创造更高的分数和记录，同时使用金币和豆子可以升级角色能力，也可以解锁更多的挑战玩法。除了跑酷以外，安排了有趣并富有挑战的游戏内容，赶快加入进来，来一场轻松又充满挑战的冒险之旅吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>任务系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成一个任务可以获得相应奖励，完成任务20分钟后会自动刷新任务。没有完成任务会在每日零点刷新，当然你也可以让系统记住任务，避免任务完成一半就自动刷新。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内有丰富的小游戏挑战，小游戏可以产出金币和豆子，还有机会（概率）获得跑酷得分加倍星星。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/45a13149432d8f31327ae020af7cdd95.poster.avif?t=1731510012\" width=494 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/45a13149432d8f31327ae020af7cdd95.webm?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/45a13149432d8f31327ae020af7cdd95.mp4?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/c9e3662be372145d52316539497955ba.poster.avif?t=1731510012\" width=494 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/c9e3662be372145d52316539497955ba.webm?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/c9e3662be372145d52316539497955ba.mp4?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/b5343af612f15aa4a7810af318a30714.poster.avif?t=1731510012\" width=494 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/b5343af612f15aa4a7810af318a30714.webm?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110420/extras/b5343af612f15aa4a7810af318a30714.mp4?t=1731510012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松又充满挑战的冒险之旅，出发！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道具系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t金币：游戏中的基本货币，用于购买角色、升级角色、解锁角色、挑战小游戏等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t磁铁：自动吸附沿途金币，提高收集效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t飞行滑翔伞：让角色短暂飞行，避开地面所有障碍并收集空中的金币。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t精灵：保护角色免受一次撞击伤害，避免游戏结束。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t双倍金币：在限定时间内收集的金币数量翻倍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作方式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t操作方式：A/D键或←→方向键控制角色左右移动，以避开障碍物或收集金币。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t跳跃： W键或↑方向键即可让角色跳跃。获得道具后，还能进行二段跳或更高难度的跳跃动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t滑行：S键或↓方向键可以让角色翻滚和加速落下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松又充满挑战的冒险之旅，出发！</p>",
